3 Exhibit 26.3 supplementary に性別・年齢を加える

  • 性別（2）ｘ年齢（6）の合計12グループの平均値をsupllementary行として加える。
.d %>% mutate("A-" = `A`-1,"B-"=B-1,"C-"=C-1,"D-"=D-1) %>% 
  mutate("A+"=M - `A-`,"B+"=M-`B-`,"C+"=M-`C-`,"D+"=M- `D-`) %>% 
  select(`A-`,`A+`,`B-`,`B+`,`C-`,`C+`,`D-`,`D+`,sex,age) %>% 
  mutate(SexAge = factor( str_c(ifelse(sex==1,"F","M"),age))) %>% select(-sex,-age) -> science.df2
science.df2 %>% group_by(SexAge) %>% summarise_each(funs = mean) %>% column_to_rownames("SexAge") -> science.sex_age.df

science.df2 %>% select(-SexAge) %>% as.data.frame() %>% rbind(science.sex_age.df) -> sci.df

5 Exhibit 26.4 European Union economic indicator

.d <- read_excel(path="EU.xls",skip = 1) # 二段重ねになってるので、chrとして読み込まれている。
## New names:
## * `` -> ...1
.d %>% slice(1:12) %>% mutate(Unemp=as.numeric(Unemp),# それを数値に直しておく。
                              GDPH = as.numeric(GDPH),
                              PCH=as.numeric(PCH),
                              PCP=as.numeric(PCP),
                              RULC=as.numeric(RULC)) %>% column_to_rownames("...1") -> Original.df
.d %>% slice(17:(17+12)) %>% mutate(Unemp=as.numeric(Unemp),
                              GDPH = as.numeric(GDPH),
                              PCH=as.numeric(PCH),
                              PCP=as.numeric(PCP),
                              RULC=as.numeric(RULC)) %>% column_to_rownames("...1") -> Ranked.df

7 Exhibit 26.5

M <- 12-1
Ranked.df %>% rownames() -> rnames
Ranked.df %>% 
  mutate("Unemp+"=`Unemp`-1,"GDPH+"=`GDPH`-1,"PCH+"=`PCH`-1,"PCP+"=`PCP`-1,"RULC+"=`RULC`-1) %>% 
  mutate("Unemp-"=M-`Unemp+`,"GDPH-"=M-`GDPH+`,"PCH-"=M-`PCH+`,"PCP-"=M-`PCP+`,"RULC-"=M-`RULC+`) %>% select(-c(1:5)) %>% as.data.frame() -> ranked.dbl.df
rownames(ranked.dbl.df) <- rnames

res.ca <- ca(ranked.dbl.df)
plot.ca(res.ca,map="rowprincipal")

fviz_ca_biplot(res.ca,map="rowprincipal",repel = TRUE) + coord_fixed(ratio = 1)

  • colどうしの位置、row同しの位置は同じなのだが、重ね合わせが違う。

8 むりやりあわせてみる。rankを逆にしたらどうなる。

  • これではない。
Original.df %>% select(Unemp) %>% unlist() %>% rank() %>% rev() -> Unemp.r
Original.df %>% select(GDPH) %>% unlist() %>% rank() %>% rev()-> GDPH.r
Original.df %>% select(PCH) %>% unlist() %>% rank() %>% rev()-> PCH.r
Original.df %>% select(PCP) %>% unlist() %>% rank() %>% rev()-> PCP.r
Original.df %>% select(RULC) %>% unlist() %>% rank() %>% rev()-> RULC.r
data.frame(Unemp.r,GDPH.r,PCH.r,PCP.r,RULC.r)　-> Ranked.df.rev
M <- 12-1
Ranked.df %>% rownames() -> rnames
Ranked.df.rev %>% 
  mutate("Unemp-"=`Unemp.r`-1,"GDPH-"=`GDPH.r`-1,"PCH-"=`PCH.r`-1,"PCP-"=`PCP.r`-1,"RULC-"=`RULC.r`-1) %>% 
  mutate("Unemp+"=M-`Unemp-`,"GDPH+"=M-`GDPH-`,"PCH+"=M-`PCH-`,"PCP+"=M-`PCP-`,"RULC+"=M-`RULC-`) %>% select(-c(1:5)) %>% as.data.frame() -> ranked.dbl.df.rev
rownames(ranked.dbl.df.rev) <- rnames

res.ca <- ca(ranked.dbl.df.rev)
plot.ca(res.ca,map="rowprincipal")
fviz_ca_biplot(res.ca,map="rowprincipal",repel = TRUE) + coord_fixed(ratio = 1)

9 *- と＊＋を入れ変えたらどうなる。 - これでExhibit 26.5 と一致した。 - 本文の説明との齟齬は、どうなるか。ただ、今の時点では、このまま訳す。2020/06/24

M <- 12-1
Ranked.df %>% rownames() -> rnames
Ranked.df %>% 
  mutate("Unemp-"=`Unemp`-1,"GDPH-"=`GDPH`-1,"PCH-"=`PCH`-1,"PCP-"=`PCP`-1,"RULC-"=`RULC`-1) %>% 
  mutate("Unemp+"=M-`Unemp-`,"GDPH+"=M-`GDPH-`,"PCH+"=M-`PCH-`,"PCP+"=M-`PCP-`,"RULC+"=M-`RULC-`) %>% select(-c(1:5)) -> temp
temp %>% colnames() -> cnames
cnames2 <- c(cnames[6:10],cnames[1:5])　#<<<- ーと＋のラベルを入れ替える
colnames(temp) <- cnames2
temp %>% as.data.frame() -> ranked.dbl.df
rownames(ranked.dbl.df) <- rnames

res.ca <- ca(ranked.dbl.df)
plot.ca(res.ca,map="rowprincipal")
fviz_ca_biplot(res.ca,map="rowprincipal",repel = TRUE) + coord_fixed(ratio = 1)
